BRIEF-Regional Manager sells 16,000 shares in Bouvet at NOK 92.00/shr 
Oct 12 Bouvet ASA : 
* Bjarte Gudmundsen, regional manager of Bouvet region Rogaland, sold 16,000 shares in Bouvet at 92.00 Norwegian crowns ($11.38) per share Source text for Eikon:
